{
  "stem": "2980.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they closed in like that and took over giant areas of Eastern Poland and the Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And everybody was caught under the Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So coming back, a lot of these people were killed on the roads by the Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And were-- the Ukrainians were, were robbing them and shooting them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they-- so those who didn't run were luckier at that point.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When we came in, the, the Germans--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were still intact.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the, the-- this was Sunday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On Wednesday, the third day, the, the, the town went up in flames in several corners-- four or five different places.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The whole town was on fire.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no fire department.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it just burned.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It burned down, the-- gutted the entire center of the town, which was the Jewish center.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Jews lived in the center of the town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, and Ukrainians and Poles lived in the periphery.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And about 14, 15 streets burned down completely.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If I see?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- burning together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The fire came--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The fire-- I remember the fire.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything was on fire till the fire came to my house, to our house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father, he was always entrepreneuring.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he grabbed buckets of water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He ran on the ladder, and he put water on our house and stopped the fire from continuing, from marching on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He figured, no matter what happens, we will have to have a place where to stay.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he stopped the fire.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the other houses burned down slowly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we kept watching the fire.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then one German came up with a tricycle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he came over, du Jude, you Jew, if this house-- if this house-- [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This house will be burned.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You'll be shot immediately.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
